# SmartTalk AI Chatbot Project

## Project Name

SmartTalk AI

## Project Overview

SmartTalk AI is an AI-powered chatbot web application built using React.js, Tailwind CSS, and Google's Gemini API.

The application allows users to ask questions and receive AI-generated responses in real time. It also stores chat history locally so conversations remain available even after refreshing the page.

---

## Technologies Used

### Frontend

* React.js
* Tailwind CSS
* JavaScript (ES6+)
* Vite

### API

* Google Gemini API

### Browser Storage

* LocalStorage

---

## Main Features

### AI Chat

Users can ask any question and receive AI-generated responses.

### Typing Effect

AI responses appear character-by-character, creating a realistic chat experience.

### Chat History

All conversations are stored using LocalStorage and remain available after page refresh.

### Responsive Design

The application works on:

* Desktop
* Tablet
* Mobile devices

### Sidebar

The sidebar displays previous conversations and allows users to:

* Start a new chat
* Clear chat history

### Auto Scroll

The chat automatically scrolls to the newest message.

